Event.name: beforeload
Event.comment: Fires before a network request is made to retrieve a data object.

Param.name: params
Param.comment: The params object passed to the {@link #load} function

Event.name: load
Event.comment: Fires before the load method's callback is called.

Param.name: arg
Param.comment: The callback's arg object passed to the {@link #load} function
